{"tid":255516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵荔景站內落雨　  乘客擔遮搭扶手梯","createTime":"2017-05-24T02:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T03:22:41.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c1df42f39465d0814d5a3543f406b1dccf21d3","tid":255516,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170524/photo/bkn-20170524095616064-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170524102205\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170524095616064-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170524102205&h=8e5aae52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港今早暴雨連連，天文台發出紅色暴雨警告信號，多區雨量逾50毫米，部分地區更可能出現水浸。港鐵荔景站疑因承受不到大雨吹襲，一扶手電梯位置漏水，水滴匆匆而下，驟眼看似水簾洞的入口，乘扶手電梯的市民也要開遮擋雨。<br />\n<br />\n有巿民拍攝到當時的情況，從照片所見，港鐵亦在扶手電梯旁放置了2個灰色膠桶，但漏水情況嚴重，膠桶很快已載滿。"},{"pid":"338e2445a87a7ff84dab7bda228ce910fd6d24d4","tid":255516,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:36:19.000Z","msg":"最左邊扶手電梯（圖片冇顯示），<br />\n啱啱好做緊更換配件工程而停運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0f7e880733abba5bbe29f37a463e71cd1c80e3","tid":255516,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加價"},{"pid":"b93f2c2ec46d51bfa227aabd1d42c112d25dfda7","tid":255516,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"水浸先係黃雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2657c2169fb0d9bf87a218eaaadd6904bf287d33","tid":255516,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706af6226ed07d3d76ef6bc269efdea58fd19df0","tid":255516,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:45:18.